data.text: I never believed that she ever got over Brad,,Hope she does NOT go back to him.

Jennifer Aniston’s hatred of New York doomed her marriage 2 Justin Theroux, friends say.The actress had tried 2 move 2 Manhattan after she fell 4 Justin, 46, who owns a place in Greenwich Village but Jen, 49, “couldn’t deal w the paparazzi & the pokey apt Jennifer is happy in LA.
